summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the sale of City real property for multifamily development; authorizing the sale of Dearborn-Hiawatha Parcel 2c in the I-90 Redevelopment Project area, at Hiawatha Place South and South Charles Street, to Artspace Projects, Inc. or its designee; authorizing the Director of the Office of Housing to execute, deliver, and administer the contract for sale of land, deed and related documents; and ratifying and confirming prior acts.
